description: Try our easy to follow Slow-Cooked Chicken Stew recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Stew,Low saturated fat,Seafood free,Healthier Easier,Winter,Low sugar,High protein,One-pot,Comfort food,Chicken
name: Slow-Cooked Chicken Stew Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 600g skinless chicken thigh fillets, halved, fat trimmed

recipeInstructions.text: Heat oil in a large saucepan over medium heat. Add chicken and paprika. Cook for 5 minutes, stirring occasionally, until chicken is browned. Add Simply Simmer Veggie Mix and cook for a further 5 minutes.

Add stock, cover saucepan and simmer on low heat for 20 minutes. Add the Woolworths Winter Veg Mix and cook for a further 10 minutes and season with pepper to taste. Divide stew among serving bowls and serve with flatbread.
